title: We Are Rockets!
overview: Wakaba is a 2nd grade high school student in Fukui Prefecture, Japan. When Wakaba was little, she admired the cheerleading club "JETS" from Fukui Chuo High School in Fukui Prefecture. She dreamed of joining the "JETS," but she thought it was impossible for her to join and enrolled at another high school. One day, a transfer student from Tokyo talks to Wakaba and proposes "let's do cheer dance together."
